<appendix id="coreValidation">
    <title>XLIFF Grammar Files</title>
    <para>The basic grammar and structure of XLIFF &version; is defined using several XML Schemas
        and one XML catalog. The module schemas are specifically referenced from their
        respective modules.</para>

    <orderedlist>
        <listitem id="CoreSchema">
            <para>XLIFF Core <olink targetdoc="../introduction/introduction.xml"
                    targetptr="XMLSchema">[XML Schema]</olink>,</para>
            <para><ulink url="&this-loc;/schemas/xliff_core_2.2.xsd"
                    >&this-loc;/schemas/xliff_core_2.2.xsd</ulink></para>

        </listitem>
        <listitem id="XLIFFCatalog">
            <para><olink targetdoc="../introduction/introduction.xml" targetptr="XMLCatalogs">[XML
                    Catalog]</olink> of XLIFF Defined XML Schemas,</para>
            <para><ulink url="&this-loc;/schemas/catalog.xml"
                >&this-loc;/schemas/catalog.xml</ulink></para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
            <para>XML Schemas of XLIFF Modules are referenced from those modules.</para>
        </listitem>
    </orderedlist>


